&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3120&quot; title=&quot;[rest] content transcoding&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-3120&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-3120&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
