&lt;p&gt;Testing&lt;br/&gt;
-------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Created a test table. Modified the HCD of a column family by adding a custom attribute of &apos;Transform$1&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;*:Base64&apos;. Used curl to store the string &quot;Testing 1, 2, 3&quot; using content type application/octet-stream. Confirmed with shell the value was base64 encoded in table. Used curl to retrieve the value using accept header of application/octet-stream and confirmed the response body was the decoded string.&lt;/p&gt;


